      • validateSubSettings

        protected abstract void validateSubSettings(org.knime.core.node.NodeSettingsRO mySettings)
                                     throws org.knime.core.node.InvalidSettingsException
        Abstract method for implementing classes to validate their settings
        Parameters:

        Throws:
